Introduction
============

Logilabvm is a Virtual Machines (VMs) manager based on libvirt <http://libvirt.org/> and virsh. It can manage different type of VMs no matter the hypervisor they are running on. This project is composed of a library and a console HMI.

Content of the project
======================

|-- bin: contains program binary
|-- conf: contains settings of the program
|-- doc: contains any usefull documentation
|-- hooks: contains default hooks
|-- hmi: contains HMI sources
|-- lib: contains library sources
|   `-- test: contains unittests for library sources
`-- scripts: contains advanced VM creation scripts
    `-- echo: contains dummy VM creation scripts

